16952447/10158442972597448/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰@旺角】情侶遭持刀斧5兇徒襲擊 女子恐毀容 警員冇拉人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191225/60414843?fbclid=IwAR0LGleFWWw-0pN0wD-3mf4uvGn5Rks-XzHfP7hHOJNTi-eRmNLA3vm66EY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F60414843%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0LGleFWWw-0pN0wD-3mf4uvGn5Rks-XzHfP7hHOJNTi-eRmNLA3vm66EY&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=e584cf53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F60414843%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0LGleFWWw-0pN0wD-3mf4uvGn5Rks-XzHfP7hHOJNTi-eRmNLA3vm66EY&h=dcf74427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191225/60414843?fbclid=IwAR0LGleFWWw-0pN0wD-3mf4uvGn5Rks-XzHfP7hHOJNTi-eRmNLA3vm66EY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20191225-22_kJ60W_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20191225-22_kJ60W_1200x0.png&h=ada0f0d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖誕夜多區衝突 警九龍灣拘約廿人 旺角持續對峙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E5%A4%9C%E5%A4%9A%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%AD%A6%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3%E6%8B%98%E7%B4%84%E5%BB%BF%E4%BA%BA-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99/?fbclid=IwAR1gRKrpOr2hEd9tPssWC1I0ekCvjhvYqsbrl5N7nfMf5DdFF8AJDI6K8sk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E5%25A4%259C%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%258B%2598%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%25BB%25BF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B3%2599%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1gRKrpOr